;THE COFACTOR 4A RESIDUES 990-1000 (GLY SER VAL VAL ILE VAL GLY ARG ILE ASN LEU) IN THIS ENTRY CORRESPOND TO RESIDUES NUMBERING 1678-1688 OF DATABASE SEQUENCE REFERENCE (UNP A8DG50). THIS PEPTIDE IS COVALENTLY LINKED TO THE N-TERMINUS OF NS3. C1679S MUTATION WAS ENGINEERED TO PREVENT DISULFIDE FORMATION. THE V1686I AND I1687N WERE ENGINEERED TO OPTIMIZE THE LINKER BETWEEN THE COFACTOR 4A AND NS3.
;
